summary:
Specialized traditional  Japanese handpoke  tattoo Tebori artisan since 2003. I use Traditional Japanese handpoke tattoo method TEBORI. It began since Edo era(about 500years ago). TEBORI is less pain and less skin damage than tattoo machine, deep and strong color, and never come out the ink.

Sponsored by 
Kro Sumi Tattoo Ink & Dermalize Pro 

Awards

•2nd place Best Of Oriental
in Convenciao De Taatuagem De Joinville, Brazil 2019
​
•Grand Prix Award(only competitor who got 1st place can entry)
•Best Of Show
•1st place Best Asian Style
in Queens City Tattoo & Art Festival 2019
 
•1st place Best of Friday in Olbia Tattoo Show 2019

•1st Prize Best of Oriental in Expo Tattoo Guadarajala in Mexico 2018

•1st Prize Best of Oriental in Amsterdam Tattoo Convention 2017

•2nd Prize Best of Oriental in Expo Tattoo Guadakajara 2016

•1st Prize Best of Color in Expo Tattoo Guadakajara 2015


•Best of Day
•1st Prize Best of Oriental Expo
•2nd Prize Best of Oriental 
in Borneo Tattoo Expo 2016

•3rd Prize Best of Ornamental in Slovenia Tattoo Convention 2016
